<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Home_theater_PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.hardware.info/en-UK/articles/am9nY2pqZA/ATI_and_nVidia_crush_highend_DVD_players/1" class="external text" title="http://www.hardware.info/en-UK/articles/am9nY2pqZA/ATI_and_nVidia_crush_highend_DVD_players/1" rel="nofollow">[ Hardware.Info ] - ATI and nVidia crush high-end DVD players</a></li>
